'''[[Aimee]] [[Louise]] [[Sword]]''' (also known as '''Aimee/Amy [[Pope]]''') is a 35 year-old [[MILF|hot mother]] with a cool name who gave her son up for adoption when he was five. [[Last Thursday|Ten years later]], in the summer of 2008, he had [[puberty|blossomed]] into a [[13-year-old boy|fifteen]] year-old [[bipolar]] [[gangbang]]er. After communicating [[online]], Aimee arranged to reconnect with her son [[IRL]] on one of his brief stints outside of [[Buttsecks|juvie]].

Once he arrived, he finally got a chance [[fuck|to get to know]] his [[cougar|mother]], so that summer they had [[incest|a family reunion]]. In the August 22-23 2008 weekend, feeling tired and chipper, Aimee knew that he had told some folks about the reunion but still loved and missed him and tried to relax. But later that night, she was almost swooped up! Relieved, she took an exam break on Tuesday, but the pathetic busybodies kept hounding her, but she strongly rose during the worst of obstacles as always.

Someone contacted CPS and they contacted the [[police]]. She surrendered on April 24, 2009. This was spread all over the internet on September 10, 2009. The resulting drama made people forget the [[9/11|big anniversary]]. The pre-trial date was set for September 21.


